    <h1>Viral Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">A promotional strategy that turns your audience into your distribution channel. When content or a product spreads person-to-person faster than you spend to acquire each viewer, your <strong>cost per reach collapses</strong> and growth compounds.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
